Package: systemd-motion
Version: 1.0.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: python3 (>= 3.10), python3-dbus-next, systemd
Recommends: python3-gi, python3-gi-cairo, gir1.2-gtk-4.0, gir1.2-adwaita-1
Maintainer: Systemd Motion Team <systemd-motion@example.com>
Description: Systemd Motion Session Manager
 Systemd Motion is a lightweight session management service that monitors
 user behavior and maintains system session state. It integrates seamlessly
 with systemd and provides silent background operation.
 .
 Features:
  - Silent session monitoring via systemd-logind
  - Minimal resource usage
  - Configurable behavior thresholds
  - Optional session simulation
  - Native systemd integration
  - Hidden operation mode
